        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Yes8 login page ဘာကြောင့် မဖွင့်တာလဲ?</h3>
          <p>Domain mirror ပြောင်းခြင်း၊ network block, cache issue, login maintenance တို့ကြောင့် ဖြစ်နိုင်ပါတယ်။ Official link ကိုစစ်ပြီး mobile data နဲ့တစ်ခါ စမ်းပါ။</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Yes8 slot bonus ကို ဘယ်လိုဖတ်ရမလဲ?</h3>
          <p>Turnover x, allowed games, max bet, bonus expiry, withdrawal cap ကို အရင်ဖတ်ပါ။ Slot အားလုံး bonus turnover ကို 100% မတွက်နိုင်ပါ။</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Yes8 APK ကို PV991 က host လုပ်ထားလား?</h3>
          <p>မလုပ်ထားပါ။ လုံခြုံရေးအတွက် APK file ကို third-party မှာမဟုတ်ဘဲ official source ထဲက link ကိုသာ စစ်ရန် အကြံပြုပါတယ်။</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@graph": [
      {
        "@type": "WebPage",
        "@id": `${siteUrl}/platforms/${platform.slug}`,
        "url": `${siteUrl}/platforms/${platform.slug}`,
        "name": title,
        "description": description,
        "inLanguage": "my-MM",
        "about": [
          { "@type": "Thing", "name": "Yes8 login" },
          { "@type": "Thing", "name": "Yes8 slot" },
          { "@type": "Thing", "name": "Yes8 APK" }
        ],
        "dateModified": "2026-06-26"
      },
      {
        "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
        "itemListElement": [
          { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "PV991", "item": siteUrl },
          { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Platforms", "item": `${siteUrl}/platforms/` },
          { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Yes8", "item": `${siteUrl}/platforms/${platform.slug}` }
        ]
      }
    ]
  })} />
</Layout>

<style>
  .container { max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem; }
  .breadcrumb { font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .breadcrumb a { color: inherit; }
  .hero { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .eyebrow { color: #ffc107; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.1rem); margin: 0 0 0.75rem; line-height: 1.25; }
  .hero p, section p { line-height: 1.85; opacity: 0.94; }
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 1.1rem; }
  .cta { display: inline-block; padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800; }
  .primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#ff3b5c,#ff6b00); color: #fff; }
  .secondary { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: #fff; }
  section { margin-top: 2.1rem; }
  h2 { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 1.45rem; }
  h3 { margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
  ul, ol { line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 1.25rem; }
  code { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem; border-radius: 6px; }
  .intent-card, .faq-item, .check-grid article {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.1rem;
  }
  .evidence-list { margin-top: 0.75rem; }
  .check-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(210px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
  .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 10px; }
  .compare-table th, .compare-table td { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); padding: 0.85rem; vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.7; }
  .compare-table th { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); text-align: left; }
  .faq-list { display: grid; gap: 1rem; }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .compare-table { display: block; overflow-x: auto; }
  }
</style>
